Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.30,0:00:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本解放战线
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.68,0:00:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了摧毁这支11区最大的武装势力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:13.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,科奈莉娅总督对成田连山展开了包围作战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.10,0:00:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在以压倒性镇压力为傲的布里塔尼亚军
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,认为形势已定之时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团开始行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使用红莲二式的辐射波动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:28.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使山中的地下水脉瞬间爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.37,0:00:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,山崩发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不论日本解放战线还是布里塔尼亚军主力部队
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.48,0:00:38.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都被泥石流卷入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,失去主力的科奈莉娅的部队被孤立了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.40,0:00:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,想要扭转情势的ZERO带领黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.80,0:00:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,将科奈莉娅作为了目标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.90,0:00:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人总是相信自己的胜利的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.64,0:01:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,然而在时间与命运的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.32,0:01:05.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,『相信』这种行为总是过于空虚  脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 11
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}成田攻防战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:41.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我军的损失怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:44.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从信号上来看损失了20%
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.29,0:02:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,20%?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:47.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来指挥系统会出问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是玛里逊队  无法与阿历克斯将军取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.84,0:02:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第2师团可以说是被全灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:55.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊德  这是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.66,0:02:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  很不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:02:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.11,0:02:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没有确定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但有黑色骑士团出现的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.08,0:03:03.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜  说不定有出场机会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.36,0:03:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太不谨慎了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:09.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要我告诉你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:13.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛  总之呢就等参谋部统合情报的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.88,0:03:20.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们再决定对应措施吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总督没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在山崩的范围之外  没有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.33,0:03:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是因为身后的部队移动了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.74,0:03:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,变成了容易被偷袭的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,纯血派在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:38.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  启动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.44,0:03:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会输给11区人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:42.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有荣耀自尊的布里塔尼亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,丘威尔卿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  红莲前往预定地点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里由剩下的人突破  瞄准科奈莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:50.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能行的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,死守住这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,杉山  还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.18,0:03:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该死  冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.98,0:04:07.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  快行动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要在这场战斗中活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就能成为战士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那前方才是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.02,0:04:14.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,纯血派阻止了他们?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:15.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.64,0:04:16.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在维蕾塔卿的指挥下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:18.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那只有趁现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让总督向后退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:20.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,空军掩护
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总督后面有什么正在接近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各机  准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无赖·改出击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出击
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:32.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.86,0:04:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这次山崩是人为造成的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:37.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应该可以到达科奈莉娅的背后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.72,0:04:38.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住科奈莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.45,0:04:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正是讨回七年前的债的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赌上我们四圣剑的名誉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.17,0:04:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,保护殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,包围起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本解放战线吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,斩击包围阵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.21,0:04:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.17,0:05:02.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要认为这只是普通的无赖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:05.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我想起七年前呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和那时候可不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:09.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我们也有KnightMare啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.42,0:05:11.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下  这里交给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.53,0:05:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请暂时后退
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就拿他们当祭品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.63,0:05:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交锋之后来九号地点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:22.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,九号?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.98,0:05:23.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.21,0:05:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,科奈莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,脆弱的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.51,0:05:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  就这样把ZERO压制住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.13,0:05:36.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  让卡莲回来会比较…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:39.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在如果变换配置的话作战会崩溃的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此情况还是很不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去就会和亲卫队交手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像科奈莉娅在下面受到了奇袭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.54,0:05:48.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.36,0:05:49.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个部队的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:51.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我们  好像是解放战线
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.44,0:05:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有看透我们这里计划的家伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:55.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:58.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么应该可以拖住亲卫队
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,少将阁下  我来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,藤堂  我等着你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.12,0:06:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,阁下  现在请把兵力全部投入
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.54,0:06:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能赢他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能压制住布里塔尼亚本队的话就能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在正是逆转战局的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听说11区有具有将军之才的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:21.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道这人就是那个藤堂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.67,0:06:22.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:29.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何都要和科奈莉亚总督汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.59,0:06:34.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  敌人的大本营就在眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.03,0:06:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且如果背后被攻击的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,部队就会出现损失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.69,0:06:38.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:39.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果失去了公主的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战斗本身就会被结束
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:42.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲米娅副总督
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让这艘G1也出击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把总督…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:52.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  吉尔弗德队长也没有动就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,科奈莉娅总督的生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:55.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里还设置了野战医院
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:02.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有周围来避难的居民
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再说  这艘G1 BASE是本阵的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:08.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总督严命无论发生什么事都不能动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:09.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…因此…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.78,0:07:13.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.55,0:07:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是特别派遣行动技术部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无礼的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是随军的非正规军给我老老实实地待着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.77,0:07:24.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就因如此所以很麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,非常闲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:29.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲米娅副总督
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.74,0:07:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请给特派命令
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:33.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太显而易见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.85,0:07:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想要得到救出总督这个功绩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.65,0:07:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果就凭一台机体就能改变状况的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:39.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都不会辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.92,0:07:41.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且只不过是个编号住民
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不不  所以说让我们试试看也好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.18,0:07:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算失败了你们那边也没什么损失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  我说你们有在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.22,0:07:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了  拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  一定不辜负您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.61,0:08:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙  真行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.87,0:08:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.77,0:08:07.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,科奈莉娅该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果ZERO是我猜的那种人的话一定会出手的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.18,0:08:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里只有相信他了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO改变行进路线了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.15,0:08:16.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:19.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在就去援助你们那边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:20.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这些还是要注意ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:21.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把路线的情报给我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是ZERO他们的预测路线
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:29.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是想把藤堂他们引去的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:30.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,科奈莉娅殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:36.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我听见了  吉尔弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.43,0:08:42.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向导兵器  Z01 Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.22,0:08:44.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使用SANDBOOT
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:47.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用最大战速沿液状斜面上升
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,救援总督
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.59,0:08:49.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes My Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.72,0:08:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀  想要问你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.73,0:08:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你极端讨厌人的死亡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.71,0:08:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但却愿意在军队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:04.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不想让人死才会在军队
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.31,0:09:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那种纯真总有一天会害死你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.34,0:09:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:13.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Lancelot  出击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:18.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,科奈莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.94,0:09:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是个无能的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:24.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不是普通的CUSTOM机
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[CUSTOM机：指一般机体的强化机种]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:33.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听见没有  科奈莉娅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:35.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经将军了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是ZERO吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.42,0:09:37.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:39.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该庆祝我们的再会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:42.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  在此之前希望你能向我们投降
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有事想要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.76,0:09:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便一说  你的援军来不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的胜利哦  科奈莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:54.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢的ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:56.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:58.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要打倒这家伙就能走上胜利之路了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.30,0:10:04.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是能干的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:18.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,从背后攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  那你是说你们的作战不卑鄙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在重整情势之前竟然受到夹击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.03,0:10:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去会到不了公主那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把敌人的援军击溃了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.84,0:10:40.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:42.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,变换旋回活杀自在阵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.23,0:10:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.40,0:10:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去科奈莉娅殿下会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.44,0:10:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的骑士吉尔弗德啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.57,0:10:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你能和达尔顿一起辅佐由菲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:10:58.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会投降
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.04,0:11:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作为一名皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有战斗到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.32,0:11:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,科…科奈莉娅大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.17,0:11:10.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  无聊的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:21.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是一样乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用VARIS把之间的障碍都毁掉这种
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总督  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,救援来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:33.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然是特派
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁允许的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:37.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是那架Lancelot的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:40.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道  那架KnightMare是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.31,0:11:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对  是新宿和河口那个时候的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是吗  又是他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.71,0:11:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,红莲二式把白壳的家伙毁掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:52.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙的突破力是个障碍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:53.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那里交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我攻击ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.61,0:12:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新宿的债我就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:12.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和Lancelot一样高速
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要打倒这个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:27.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就凭这种武器
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,挡下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.83,0:12:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,扇  红莲怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:56.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,右手不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不修理的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全军  向撤退路线移动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再下去会成为消耗战
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.92,0:13:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总督
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你去追ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:12.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:14.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只不过是能源没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.67,0:13:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:16.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:21.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  撤退真的好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.24,0:13:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赢了已经是事实了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.78,0:13:24.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有把日本解放战线作为诱饵  逃走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.63,0:13:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我讨厌这种说法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.15,0:13:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:34.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人类不是游戏的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.63,0:13:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO应该也不是这样想的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.75,0:13:39.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也成了棋盘上被使用的棋子了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.11,0:13:44.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.77,0:13:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他对于布里塔尼亚的愤怒是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:51.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知晓愤怒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:53.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该也知晓悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:00.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,特派报告
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:01.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发现ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.37,0:14:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始俘获
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:14.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO  你有恩于我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你的行动也有人被救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也知道很多11区住民在背后支持你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,错了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是  新宿的  密封舱里的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.70,0:14:37.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.55,0:14:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要对这个男人出手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.50,0:14:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:42.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她是  ZERO的同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:47.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.28,0:14:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对方是KnightMare啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:51.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你死了我会很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:53.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然只是间接接触
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也有尝试一下的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:15.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,应该已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:24.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:25.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有那种意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:28.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:33.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  难道你对驾驶员使用Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只是给他看打击影像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他看到了些什么我可不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:39.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这些  快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.78,0:15:41.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在不能动
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你先走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不停地欠着你的情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手  现在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  和之前的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:15.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要到我的里面来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:22.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我  被打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.74,0:16:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只能那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.00,0:16:56.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.29,0:16:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:16:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:00.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点…逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:07.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要追
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的行动停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.06,0:17:13.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在和少将他们汇合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,协助他们逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.79,0:17:17.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,殿下  我现在就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔弗德  通报全军
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,准备撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.71,0:17:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没有理由再赌上我们将士的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:27.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,维持战斗态势
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,缓缓撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能不承认
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.94,0:17:34.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是我们输了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.97,0:17:39.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚要对付解放战线已经竭尽全力了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.17,0:17:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  我们也确实得到了逃跑的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.93,0:17:48.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我说ZERO呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和无赖无法联系
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道被抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个女人  果然不是人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伤口的再生速度不一般
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,新宿的时候的确也被击中了额头
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是克洛维斯私下在研究的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.47,0:18:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和布里塔尼亚应该没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:13.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,vital sign和人类一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:14.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[vital sign：生命征兆 如脉搏 呼吸 体温 心跳等]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:16.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,血液样本稍后再检查
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:18.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伤口也拍一下照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:32.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你终于叫我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是没有抓住ZERO吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:46.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本解放战线设下了防卫线
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.65,0:18:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是混在里面了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.20,0:18:51.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总是把什么当作盾牌来保护自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.00,0:18:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,枢木怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经回收了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.49,0:18:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等到他能量耗尽之前一直在等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.18,0:18:59.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以多花了点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.69,0:19:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,机体状态不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.55,0:19:03.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为处于暴走状态
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.46,0:19:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不像是哥哥部队该有的失态呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经把碎片取出了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.20,0:19:15.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也帮你洗过伤口了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.57,0:19:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看样子的确是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:21.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你不需要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.22,0:19:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是在无聊的地方执著于自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.86,0:19:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏这样知道了些好事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:35.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,兴趣真坏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偷听这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,挺好的名字嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:43.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比C.C.像人类多了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:44.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说我像人类
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.05,0:19:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.18,0:19:51.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.86,0:19:54.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全部
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.56,0:19:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.02,0:19:59.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到现在名字这种
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,名字…什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是个好机会所以我说一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:11.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:12.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止也一直是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.92,0:20:18.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,包括Geass的事也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.73,0:20:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.93,0:20:22.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.95,0:20:25.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是第一次被人感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.95,0:20:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你要还礼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再叫一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:39.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像刚才一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那个名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要一次
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.41,0:20:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,重视的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:47.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,温柔的包含心意的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.67,0:20:50.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.14,0:21:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行呢  完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:06.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不够温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.34,0:21:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直率与体贴的心意也不够
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,发音也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:12.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的是缺少温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.75,0:21:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个任性的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:15.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本来就是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我是C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.19,0:21:29.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又是军人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.77,0:21:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说明部队崩溃到这种程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是ORANGE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.04,0:21:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.00,0:21:47.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,迎接的人貌似来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.32,0:21:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.20,0:21:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的成员先…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.24,0:21:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:56.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.79,0:21:59.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她是我重要的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.73,0:22:05.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我不知道雪为什么是白的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.06,0:22:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但我认为白色的雪很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.49,0:22:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.64,0:22:13.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.69,0:23:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.32,0:23:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把科奈莉娅逼入绝境的某种条件
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.67,0:23:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了弥补这个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.48,0:24:00.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能我自己必须跨越某种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.68,0:24:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.43,0:24:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,必须前往该去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.96,0:24:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.07,0:24:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果为此这是必须的话  我…
